{"tid":1338043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘朋友請尋找狗總秘密通道","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:11:07.000Z","uid":243262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d751d124399b43589550f8fcca477ee9507b28c1","tid":1338043,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師之愚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有大量警力濟留政總狗總內部<br />\n本身無人衝佢地都無必要出黎<br />\n但支聯辦突然被圍會唔會製造左壓力令佢地要出黎增援?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係狗總出黎無可避免要先驅散人群<br />\n所以呢個時候會唔會捨易取難<br />\n動用秘密通道出黎??<br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩係金鐘迷惘緊唔知做乜好既朋友<br />\n可以襯依家人仲多<br />\n到停車場留意下d水電房門有無人士大量出入<br />\n如果真係有秘密出入口<br />\n咁既舉動都可以拖一拖狗既調動速度<br />\n幫到係西環既戰友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b3c6a20c9d680cbb831a90428eae03551ac4a0","tid":1338043,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff7630099c485be5435b3815aa40a8c77f7d5ddf","tid":1338043,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cc2195f26926e7d0f15ea23e5973963dc983e9d","tid":1338043,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}